===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# {{transitive}} To [[say]] or [[write]] (something) using particular words.
#: ''I’m not sure how to '''word''' this letter to the council.''

====Synonyms====
* {{sense|say or write using particular words}} [[express]], [[phrase]], [[put into words]], [[state]]

