# {{historical}} A unit of [[currency]] formerly used in France, divided into 20 [[sol]]s or [[sou]]s. #* '''1992''', Hilary Mantel, ''A Place of Greater Safety'', Harper Perennial 2007, p. 115: #*: They like to see them awarded comfortable pensions. Is it 700,000 '''livres''' a year to the Polignac family?
