===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{semantics}} A word which has the [[opposite]] meaning of another, although not necessarily in all its senses.
#: ''"rich" is an '''antonym''' of "poor"; "full" is an '''antonym''' of "empty"''.

====Antonyms====
* [[synonym]]

