===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun}}

# {{grammar}} A [[word]] that [[modify|modifies]] a noun or [[describe]]s a noun’s referent.
#: ''The words “big” and “heavy” are English '''adjectives'''.''

====Hyponyms====
* See also [[Wikisaurus:adjective]]

