* French: {{t+|fr|Fabien}}
* German: {{t+|de|Fabian}}
{{trans-mid}}
* Italian: {{t+|it|Fabiano}}
* Spanish: {{t-|es|Fabián}}
* Swedish: {{t+|sv|Fabian}}
{{trans-bottom}}

