===Etymology=== From {{etyl|LL.}} {{term|abacinatus|abacinātus||lang=la}}, perfect passive participle of {{term|abacino|abacinō||lang=la}}; possibly formed from {{term|ab||off|lang=la}} + {{term|bacinum|bacīnum|a basin|lang=la}} or {{term|bacinus|bacīnus|lang=la}}. Probably cognate with modern Italian {{term|abbacinare||to dazzle|lang=it}}.
