===Etymology=== "Name given by the [[negro]]es in the island of [[St. Thomas]]" - ''Webster, 1913'' * '''Note''' This editor has not yet been able to identify the exact plant intended. The name may have origins in the [[Fang]] language of [[Gabon]].
