# [[into]] [[that]], [[to]] [[that]], [[there]] #: '''''Abba''' a dobozba rakd a ruhákat.'' - Put the clothes '''into that''' box.
====Usage notes==== It points to the inside of an object that is farther away from the speaker. Its opposite pair is [[ebbe]] which points to the inside of an object close to the speaker.
