# {{plants}} An [[evergreen]] shrub (''[[Hibiscus]]'' -- formerly ''Abelmoschus -- moschatus''), of the East and West Indies and Northern Africa, whose [[musky]] seeds are used in [[perfumery]] and to flavor [[coffee]]; -- sometimes called ''[[musk mallow]]''.

