#*: {{...}} se contentant d'annoncer que l''''ablation''' des nouvelles permettra de voguer vers «la production d'émissions culturelles et de divertissement de qualité». — ''merely announcing that the elimination of news programming [on tv channel [[w:TQS|TQS]]] will allow it to focus on "the production of quality entertainment and cultural programming"''
