==English==
===Pronunciation=== * {{a|UK}} {{IPA|/ˈæ.bə.lɪʃn̩.ɪst/}}, {{SAMPA|1=/"{.b@.lISn=.Ist/}} * {{a|US}} {{SAMPA|/{'b@lI"S@n@st/}}
