==English==
===Etymology=== Derivative of [[abort]]
===Adjective=== {{en-adj|-}}
# Brought forth [[prematurely]]. # {{biology}} Rendered [[abortive]] or [[sterile]]; [[undeveloped]]; checked in normal development at a very early stage; as, spines are ''aborted'' branches. #: ''"The eyes of the cirripeds are more or less '''aborted''' in their mature state."'' -[[w:Richard Owen|Richard Owen]].
