===Alternative forms===
* {{l|en|abowt}} {{qualifier|archaic}}

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}} {{term|aboute|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang}} {{term|abutan|abūtan|lang=ang}}, {{term|onbutan|onbūtan|on, about, around, round about, on the outside|lang=ang}}, from {{term|on||on|lang=ang}} + {{term|butan|būtan|outside|lang=ang}}; equivalent to {{l|en|on}} + {{l|en|be-}} + {{l|en|outen}}. More at {{l|en|but}}, {{l|en|outen}}.

